CONTEXT GibraltarBB IN ENGLISH
PURPOSE CONTEXT GibraltarBB
{+ Models the structure of an FC5 classifier _ast.yml (export requirements per country),
   so a population extracted from such a file imports flawlessly — at run time (upload of
   GibraltarBB.yml) and at compile time (INCLUDE, see GibraltarBB.adl). The relations mirror
   the keys of Gibraltar_Bloembollen_exporteisen_1.0_ast.yml. No RULEs, so no invariant can
   block the import. +}

REPRESENT Text TYPE BIGALPHANUMERIC

CONCEPT Land "A country/territory a requirements document is about"
CONCEPT CertificateRequirement "A certificate requirement entry"
CONCEPT CropRequirement "A crop requirement entry"
CONCEPT RequirementGroup "A group of requirements combined by a logical operator"
CONCEPT Requirement "A single requirement"
CONCEPT Crop "A crop or plant product"
CONCEPT Heading "A heading in the source document outline"
CONCEPT Operator "A logical operator combining requirements (e.g. AND)"
CONCEPT RequirementType "The type of a requirement (e.g. Other)"

-- Land level (certificateRequirements / cropRequirements in the yml)
RELATION certificateRequirement[Land*CertificateRequirement]
RELATION cropRequirement[Land*CropRequirement]

-- Certificate requirement fields. The three booleans are PROP relations: present = true.
RELATION exportCertificate[CertificateRequirement*CertificateRequirement] [PROP]
RELATION reExportCertificate[CertificateRequirement*CertificateRequirement] [PROP]
RELATION importPermit[CertificateRequirement*CertificateRequirement] [PROP]
RELATION appliesTo[CertificateRequirement*Text] [UNI]

-- Crop requirement fields
RELATION crop[CropRequirement*Crop]
RELATION requirementGroup[CropRequirement*RequirementGroup]

-- Requirement group fields
RELATION operator[RequirementGroup*Operator] [UNI]
RELATION sourceHeading[RequirementGroup*Heading]
RELATION requirement[RequirementGroup*Requirement]

-- Requirement fields
RELATION requirementType[Requirement*RequirementType] [UNI]
RELATION method[Requirement*Text] [UNI]
RELATION remarks[Requirement*Text] [UNI]

INTERFACE Landen : V[SESSION*Land] BOX
  [ "certificaateisen" : certificateRequirement
  , "gewaseisen"       : cropRequirement
  ]

ENDCONTEXT
